summary:
Software Test Engineer with over 8 years of experience in Software Development field, working on enterprise software products. Experience emphasized on Manual and Automation Testing with Selenium Framework, Cucumber/Behave, Java/Python, TestNG, Postman and Jenkins. 

My other skills include: fast learning, teamwork, self-motivation, self-taught, researching, participating and organization of tech events.
